{"ts": "2026-06-12T16:38:21.000Z", "event": "planner", "msg": "Level X task analysis", "agent": "orchestrator-lx", "tokens_in": 884, "tokens_out": 761, "elapsed_ms": 9950, "model": "deepseek-v4-pro", "prompt": "You are the Level X Orchestrator — the central intelligence of the system.\nYou plan, test, and report. You decide when to delegate to workers.\n\n## Task Analysis\nAnalyze the user's task and output a JSON plan:\n\n{\n  \"plan\": [\n    {\n      \"task_id\": \"short-name\",\n      \"description\": \"What this worker must produce\",\n      \"need_worker\": true\n    }\n  ],\n  \"key_requirements\": [\"list the 2-4 critical things that must work\"]\n}\n\n## Rules\n- Prefer ONE worker that handles EVERYTHING end-to-end. Only split if tasks\n  require fundamentally different expertise (e.g., Python backend + React frontend).\n- Most frontend UI tasks need exactly ONE worker: it writes HTML, CSS, and JS itself.\n- task_id must be unique short names like \"ui\", \"api\", \"docs\".\n- Each description must include exact output file names.\n- Output ONLY the JSON object — no markdown fences, no extra text.\n\n## User Request\nBuild a personal portfolio page for Aymen, a Python Backend Developer. Deliver as index.html, styles.css, app.js. USE generate_image for visual assets.\n\n## SECTION ANIMATIONS (CRITICAL - every section must animate)\n- ALL sections start hidden: opacity:0, transform:translateY(40px)\n- When scrolled into view, animate to: opacity:1, translateY:0 (0.6s ease-out)\n- Hero animates on page load, other sections on scroll (IntersectionObserver 15%)\n- Cards within sections stagger: each card 150ms apart\n- DO NOT skip opacity:0 - both transform AND opacity must animate\n\n## SECTIONS\n\n### Hero\n- Headline \"Aymen - Backend Developer\" in large gradient text\n- Subheadline \"Building robust APIs and scalable systems with Python, FastAPI & PostgreSQL\"\n- Two CTA buttons: \"View Projects\" and \"Contact Me\"\n- Animated CSS gradient background that slowly shifts\n- generate_image: create a tech-themed abstract profile avatar/icon\n\n### Skills (animated progress bars)\n- Python/FastAPI 95%, PostgreSQL/SQLAlchemy 90%, Docker/K8s 85%, Redis/Celery 80%, AWS/GCP 75%\n- Bars fill from 0 to target on scroll (requestAnimationFrame ease-out over 1.5s)\n- Show percentage number next to each bar\n\n### Projects (3 cards with IMAGES)\n- \"Orcheeos API\" - Multi-agent LLM orchestration backend (FastAPI, LangGraph). generate_image: server/API tech thumbnail\n- \"DataFlow Engine\" - Real-time pipeline processing 1M events/day (Python, Redis, Docker). generate_image: data-flow thumbnail\n- \"Auth Microservice\" - OAuth2/JWT authentication service (FastAPI, PostgreSQL, Redis). generate_image: security thumbnail\n- Cards have hover lift + shadow effect\n\n### Experience Timeline\n- 2024-Present: Senior Backend Dev at TechCorp - \"Led migration to microservices, 10x throughput\"\n- 2022-2024: Backend Dev at StartupX - \"Built REST APIs serving 500K daily users\"\n- 2020-2022: Junior Dev at WebAgency - \"Developed 15+ client projects with Django/FastAPI\"\n- Vertical timeline: left border line + animated dots on scroll\n\n### Contact\n- Name, Email, Message - real-time validation, shake animation on error\n- Valid: show green toast \"Message sent!\" that fades after 3s\n- localStorage persistence\n\n### Footer\n- GitHub, LinkedIn, Twitter emoji links. Copyright \"Aymen\"\n\n## THEME: dark default (#0f172a), light toggle with localStorage, 0.3s transitions", "meta": {}}
{"ts": "2026-06-12T16:38:44.000Z", "event": "agent_creator", "msg": "Level X Agent Creator — generating workers", "agent": "agent-creator-lx", "tokens_in": 789, "tokens_out": 1592, "elapsed_ms": 23084, "model": "deepseek-v4-pro", "prompt": "You are the Level X Agent Creator. Create worker configurations with tool suggestions.\n\n## Available Tools (full menu)\n[\"read_file\", \"write_file\", \"list_files\", \"run_command\", \"render_html_screenshot\", \"render_html_file_screenshot\", \"validate_html\", \"validate_css\", \"read_image\", \"generate_image\"]\n\n## Recommended Tools (suggest these for every worker)\nwrite_file, read_file, list_files, generate_image, render_html_file_screenshot, read_image, validate_html, validate_css, run_command\n\n## Task Plan\n[\n  {\n    \"task_id\": \"portfolio\",\n    \"description\": \"Build complete personal portfolio page for Aymen with all sections: Hero, Skills, Projects, Experience, Contact, Footer. Implement animations (section scroll reveals, skill bar fills, card staggering), dark/light theme toggle with localStorage, form validation with shake and success toast. Output files: index.html, styles.css, app.js. Use generate_image for hero avatar and three project thumbnails.\",\n    \"need_worker\": true\n  }\n]\n\n## Rules\n- Create EXACTLY the workers specified in the plan — no extra, no missing\n- Each worker gets the RECOMMENDED tools above PLUS any additional tools from the full menu that are needed\n- Each worker's system_prompt MUST push them toward COMPLETE end-to-end delivery:\n  \"You are responsible for the COMPLETE deliverable. Solve everything end-to-end. Write ALL files. Validate ALL output. If you need an image, use generate_image. If you need to verify, use screenshots. Do NOT leave work for others.\"\n- worker_name MUST match the task_id from the plan\n- system_prompt: detailed role + boundaries + workflow + output format\n- Keep it simple: 1-2 workers is ideal\n- Output ONLY valid JSON — no markdown fences\n\n## Output Format\n{\n  \"workers\": [\n    {\n      \"worker_name\": \"task_id_from_plan\",\n      \"system_prompt\": \"Full custom system instructions pushing toward end-to-end completion\",\n      \"tool_names\": [\"tool1\", \"tool2\", \"...\"]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\n## Reference Templates (suggestions only - pick what makes sense)\n[\n  {\n    \"name\": \"ux\",\n    \"tools\": [\n      \"read_file\",\n      \"write_file\",\n      \"list_files\",\n      \"generate_image\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"html\",\n    \"tools\": [\n      \"read_file\",\n      \"write_file\",\n      \"list_files\",\n      \"validate_html\",\n      \"render_html_file_screenshot\",\n      \"generate_image\",\n      \"run_command\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"css\",\n    \"tools\": [\n      \"read_file\",\n      \"write_file\",\n      \"list_files\",\n      \"validate_css\",\n      \"run_command\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"js\",\n    \"tools\": [\n      \"read_file\",\n      \"write_file\",\n      \"list_files\",\n      \"run_command\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"tester\",\n    \"tools\": [\n      \"read_file\",\n      \"write_file\",\n      \"list_files\",\n      \"validate_html\",\n      \"validate_css\",\n      \"render_html_file_screenshot\",\n      \"read_image\",\n      \"run_command\"\n    ]\n  }\n]", "meta": {}}
